              </Glosses>
              <Comments>ἀνάστασις in {S:04200203400036} may also be interpreted merely as a change for the better (see {D:13.60}).|Reversals of rank and status are a frequent theme in the declaration of the prophets, and this becomes particularly significant in the Magnificat (see {S:04200104600000}).</Comments>
